            "title": "德祥地產折讓逾12%配股",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">德祥地產(00199)宣布配股，配股價0.89元，較上日收市價0.91元折讓12.09%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">配售股份數量為擴大後已發行股本6.35%，預期集資額為5531萬元，集資淨額5287萬元。</p>\n</div>",
